author: Kristina Wong
title: Taiwan Pledges 100,000 Masks Per Week for the U.S.
description: While China has begun an information campaign to try to blame coronavirus on the U.S., Taiwan has pledged to send 100,000 masks per week.
content:
While Chinese officials have begun an information campaign to try to blame the spread of coronavirus on the United States, Taiwan has stepped up to help the U.S., pledging to send 100,000 surgical face masks per week.
